Insider Activity


Individual




Randy A. Foutch



Mr. Randy A. Foutch is Independent Director at Helmerich & Payne, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Laredo Petroleum, Inc., a Member at The National Petroleum Council, a Member at Americas Natural Gas Alliance, a Member at C.M. Russell Museum, and Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Laredo Petroleum LLC. He is on the Board of Directors at Helmerich & Payne, Inc., The Catholic Foundation of Eastern Oklahoma, Inc., University of Tulsa, Leadership Oklahoma, and The Gilcrease Museum National Board.
Mr. Foutch was previously employed as Independent Non-Executive Director by Cheniere Energy, Inc., Chairman & Chief Executive Officer by Laredo Petroleum, Inc., Independent Director by Bill Barrett Corp., President & Chief Executive Officer by Latigo Petroleum, Inc., President by Lariat Petroleum, Inc., a Manager-Rocky Mountain Region by Anschutz Co., and Vice President-Exploration by Dyco Petroleum Corp. He also served on the board at MacroSolve, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Texas and a graduate degree from the University of Houston.



